<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.10.9">
<l>kōvai yiṉtamiḻ pāṭuvār kuṭa māṭu vārtaṭa māmalar micai</l>
<l>mēvu nāṉmuka ṉilviḷaṅ kupuri nūlar</l>
<l>mēvu nāṉmaṟai vāṇarai vakai vēḷvi yāṟaṅkam vallavar toḻum</l>
<l>tēva tēvapi rāṉtiruk kōṭṭiyū rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord, god of gods worshipped by those who sing verses in sweet Tamil,</l>
<l rend="indent">pot dancers,</l>
<l>Those with the sacred thread who shine like four-faced [Brahma]</l>
<l rend="indent">who dwells on a huge, broad lotus,</l>
<l>Those whose living is by the cherished four Vedas,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] those who have mastered</l>
<l>The five kinds of sacrifice and six branches [of knowledge]</l>
<l rend="indent">is the one in Tirukkōṭṭiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
